{"tid":2423663,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"梁凌杰死因預審父母沒現身 警方未能聯絡 研訊主任呼籲致電法庭","createTime":"2021-02-26T04:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T05:07:12.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8a6756f86ae9ac90a017c0965bfd296f98d3a47f","tid":2423663,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:53:21.000Z","msg":"前年6月16日反修例大遊行前夕，35歲男子梁凌杰在金鐘太古廣場高處掛上標語，其間墮樓身亡。死因庭將為他召開死因研訊，今早閉門進行研訊前檢討。據了解，研訊暫定今年5月10日至26日進行，預計有逾30名證人，並有多個有利害關係人士或團體，包括警務處處長、消防處處長，以及太古廣場等。梁凌杰的父母今早沒有到庭，警方也未能聯絡他們。死因研訊主任呼籲梁的父母聯絡法庭。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210226/QJLWJBBJ3BE37BUU33INRP774Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210226%2FQJLWJBBJ3BE37BUU33INRP774Q%2F&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd6%2FUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=6417eebc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210226%2FQJLWJBBJ3BE37BUU33INRP774Q%2F&h=de5d968a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210226/QJLWJBBJ3BE37BUU33INRP774Q/</a>"},{"pid":"9a6157f9b506e66add89b30117606f2ccb0cf4bf","tid":2423663,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:55:00.000Z","msg":"走咗啦,on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99a8dbcbb1d9473e3b8dfa807220af1715161e7","tid":2423663,"uid":100772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:07:12.000Z","msg":"傳聞個陣成班黑警係上面話要打鳩佢 又叫佢快d跳"}]}